            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "In calculating of NU, the following were taken into",
                "account:",
                "- angular correlation of fission neutrons and incident",
                "neutrons arising as a consequence of fragments angular",
                "anisotropy;",
                "- the variation of mean energy of fission neutrons with",
                "increasing NU and the difference between Cf-252",
                "fission-neutron spectrum ( used for calibration) and",
                "U-238 fission-neutron spectrum;",
                "- the neutron multiplication in the sample."
              ]
